div1.p: United States of America, Western District of Washington} ss:

I hereby certify and return that I served the annexed Application fro Writ of Habeas Corpus on the therein-named HENRY M. WHITE Com of Immigration at Seattle Wash by handing to anf leaving a true and correct copy thereof with J.H. Sargent assistant Com. of Immigration personally at Seattle Wash. in said District on the 8th day of July, A.D. 1916
John M. Boyle U.S. Marshal. By A Rooks Deputy.
